History
=======

0.3.0
-----

* run_process() renamed to run()
* Python3 compatibility fixes

0.2.0 (2018-03-12)
------------------

* Procrunner is now Python3 3.3-3.6 compatible.

0.1.0 (2018-03-12)
------------------

* First release on PyPI.


